text: Alexander Gennadyevich Zhurbin (; born 14 January 1992) is a Russian tennis player. == Tennis career == Zhurbin has a career high ATP singles ranking of 555 achieved on 3 April 2017. He also has a career high ATP doubles ranking of 565 achieved on 13 October 2014. Zhurbin has won 1 ITF Futures singles title and 4 ITF Futures doubles titles. Zhurbin made his ATP main draw debut at the 2010 St. Petersburg Open. == External links == * * Category:1992 births Category:Living people Category:Russian male tennis players
